									<section id="getting_started">
										<h2>Introduction</h2>
										<h4 class="title">
											Techguru - Technology & IT Solutions With Ecommerce & POS System Laravel CMS
										</h4>
										<p>We would like to thank you for choosing TechGuru - Technology & IT Solutions
											Laravel CMS.</p>
										<p> TechGuru – Technology & IT Solutions Laravel CMS is a Modern, Creative, and
											Responsive. CMS Design suitable for created especially for start-up, IT
											Solutions, Agencies, Marketing, Consulting and Services Company related any
											business website.
											This Cms includes 03 different homepage demo with 34+ html pages carefully
											designed blocks, which are easy to edit and customize to fit your needs.
											This Cms is perfect solution for the create of unique Technology & IT
											Solutions websites.
											TechGuru CMS has a fully responsive layout. It fits perfectly on various
											displays and resolutions from regular desktop screens to tablets, iPads,
											iPhones, and small mobile devices.
										</p>
										<!-- End of #getting_started -->
										<section>
											<h3>Getting started</h3>
											<p> You need to have a few things ready before you can start using TechGuru
												-
												Technology & IT Solutions Laravel CMS. Please make sure you have the
												following:
											</p>

											<div class="steps-panel">
												<ul class="ordered-list">
													<li>
														You need composer to install the theme.
													</li>
													<li>
														You need php 8.1+ to install the theme.
													</li>
													<li>
														You need Node 18+ with npm to install the theme.
													</li>
												</ul>
											</div>
										</section>
									</section>

