									<section id="common_issues_install">
										<h3>Some Common Issues & Solutions In Installation</h3>
										<p>
											Here are some common issues and solutions in installation:
											<br>
											In Installation, you may face some issues, Like 404 error, 500 error, etc.
											<div class="steps-panel">
												<ul class="ordered-list">
													<li> Manualy Put The Files</li>
													<div class="steps-panel">
														<ul class="ordered-list">
															<li>.env File In The Root Directory (in not have .env file
																copy from .env.example)</li>
															<li>After thet put given mysql files in your maked
																phpMyAdmin</li>
															<li>After thet copy given instald file in your storage
																folder</li>
															<li>Some time you may run some command in your terminal</li>
														</ul>
													</div>
													</li>
												</ul>
											</div>
										</p>

