									<section id="writable_issues_install">
										<h3>Writable Issues In Installatio and Solutions</h3>
										<p>
											Here are some common issues and solutions in installation:
											<br>
											In Installation, You may face some issues, Like Writable issues, etc.
											<br>
											You can fix this issue by following the steps below:
											<br>
											Step 1: Go to the root directory of the project.
											<br>
											Step 2: Run the command: chmod -R 777 storage/
										</p>
